OL,3,CActor Warwick Davis' wife Samantha
OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,FActor Warwick Davis has paid tribute
OL,7,Fto his wife and 'favourite human,' who
OL,8,Fdied on March 24, saying 'I miss her
OL,9,Fhugs.'
OL,11,FSamantha Davis, the wife of Star Wars
OL,12,Fand Harry Potter actor Warwick Davis,
OL,13,Fhas died aged 53.
OL,15,FWarwick announced the news in a
OL,16,Fstatement shared to the BBC, revealing
OL,17,Fshe had died on March 24.
