OL,3,CActor Warwick Davis' wife Samantha
OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,FSamantha co-founded the dwarfism
OL,7,Fcharity Little People UK and featured
OL,8,Fin the final Harry Potter film,
OL,9,Falongside Warwick.
OL,11,F"Her passing has left a huge hole in
OL,12,Four lives as a family. I miss her
OL,13,Fhugs," Warwick said in the statement
OL,14,Fto the BBC.
OL,16,FHe added that she was his "most
OL,17,Ftrusted confidant and an ardent
OL,18,Fsupporter of everything I did in my
OL,19,Fcareer".
