OL,6,FThe actor continued: "She was a unique
OL,7,Fcharacter, always seeing the sunny
OL,8,Fside of life she had a wicked sense of
OL,9,Fhumour and always laughed at my bad
OL,10,Fjokes."
OL,12,FThe couple met on the set of George
OL,13,FLucas's film Willow and married three
OL,14,Fyears later in 1991.
OL,16,FSamantha also played a goblin in Harry
OL,17,FPotter And The Deathly Hallows: Part 2
OL,18,Fwhile her husband played both
OL,19,FProfessor Flitwick and the goblin
OL,20,FGriphook in all eight films in the
OL,21,Ffranchise.
