OL,6,FTheir two children together, Annabelle
OL,7,Fand Harrison, also paid tribute to
OL,8,Ftheir mother, saying: "Her love and
OL,9,Fhappiness carried us through our whole
OL,10,Flives"
OL,12,F"Mum is our best friend and we're
OL,13,Fhonoured to have received a love like
OL,14,Fhers."
