OL,3,CActor Warwick Davis' wife Samantha
OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,FIn an interview with People in 2022,
OL,7,FWarwick opened up about the grief he
OL,8,Fand Samantha went through after their
OL,9,Ffirst son died shortly after he was
OL,10,Fborn due to complications from the
OL,11,Fdwarfism genes he inherited from both
OL,12,Fof his parents.
OL,14,FHe told the US outlet: "I think it
OL,15,Fbrings you closer together, or
OL,16,Fsomething like that. But it's an
OL,17,Fexperience I wouldn't wish on anyone.
OL,18,FIt's devastating."
