OL,4,Cdied aged 53
OL,6,FA few years later they experienced
OL,7,Fmore heartbreak when Samantha had a
OL,8,Fmiscarriage with their second child.
OL,10,FThey later welcomed their daughter
OL,11,FAnnabelle and son Harrison, with
OL,12,FWarwick saying the couple loved their
OL,13,Fchildren "all that more because
OL,14,Fthey're here with us".
OL,16,FAnnabelle, 27, has followed in her
OL,17,Fparents' acting footsteps, starring in
OL,18,FCBBC's The Dumping Ground and Channel
OL,19,F4 soap Hollyoaks.
