OL,6,FWarwick starred as the titular hero
OL,7,FWillow Ufgood in the 1988 original
OL,8,Ffilm Willow and reprised the role for
OL,9,Fthe 2022 sequel.
OL,11,FHe also played several characters in
OL,12,Fthe Star Wars film series.
OL,14,FSamantha and Warwick co-founded Little
OL,15,FPeople UK in 2012 to help individuals
OL,16,Fwith dwarfism and their families.
